data.description: This delightful Traditional enjoys an enviable location in the Wakefield Plantation area. A mere stone's throw from nearby schools, and only a 'jiffy' from the natural allurements of Forest Ridge Park, shopping/dining options, and more. This captivating 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom charmer displays a Traditional home's familiar proportions and sight lines, low-maintenance yard, and hardwood flooring throughout the entire 1st floor. Serene master bedroom and the other two bedrooms are ready for your decorative expertise. Water heater replaced in 2018, Dishwasher replaced in 2022. Don't miss this unique opportunity!
